metadata.name: Euh What?
metadata.description:
This image represents audition, comprehension, and communication; this is an organ of Corti. 

It symbolizes a shift in state, a physical signal that becomes an electrical signal that the brain can understand. 
It is this door that allows people to communicate with one another. 

I took this photo when I was a young pharmacologist a very long time ago.

Le cadeau: 
Use ARTIVIVE app on your phone and point it to the piece on your screen.
